{"tid":145182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會否回港支持媽媽？　林節思：要返工，不了","createTime":"2017-03-06T05:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T05:46:58.000Z","uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08ea0959b210aedfa5c785fa937266386c35b695","tid":145182,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"特首候選人林鄭月娥今晚出席民主思路舉辦的選舉論壇後，本報記者在北京偶遇林太的大兒子林節思。林節思晚上約9時半從北京「芳草地」步出，被問到如何看父親林兆波支持媽媽但被外界批評、選舉投票日前會否再回香港支持媽媽等，林節思僅以自己明早要上班，已叫車為由，未有作任何回應，向記者報以微笑後離開。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170305/s00001/1488724897064#sthash.JZRVKYS8.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170305%2Fs00001%2F1488724897064%23sthash.JZRVKYS8.dpuf&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a648eb7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170305%2Fs00001%2F1488724897064%23sthash.JZRVKYS8.dpuf&h=8422fd53\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170305/s00001/1488724897064#sthash.JZRVKYS8.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"64783d81e85a00dc06e48bdcdb37c64fd9816115","tid":145182,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"要返工 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da73a65cdc7dc83fb10021368b9e9b917a9f7b84","tid":145182,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"人質黎？"},{"pid":"202fd21d1121fd74eedce3491601a79340291db7","tid":145182,"uid":64095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"親親我老媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc868779c90491f995b7fb942a7a3c4d68e9e9d","tid":145182,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T05:11:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭選特首